 condition were imaged. Scale bars represent 100 µm. Excitation and emission wavelengths were 408/450 nm for Hoescht 33342, 488/515 nm for AlexaFluor 488 and 561/605 nm for AlexaFluor 594. Antibody dilutions and product information are listed in Additional file  2 : Table S5.

